{"tid":2335444,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[live]埼玉縣拉麵名店 寿製麺よしかわ","createTime":"2020-12-22T01:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T00:02:48.000Z","uid":8203,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b6656bd03a53955b9436a7e4a63f4c02fed33312","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T01:57:21.000Z","msg":"寿製麺 よしかわ 川越店<br />\n日本、〒350-1151 埼玉県川越市今福１７３８&minus;１４<br />\n+81 49-293-8609<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/mJTmYLCGV6bhj1Y46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FmJTmYLCGV6bhj1Y46&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=bd9066ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/mJTmYLCGV6bhj1Y46</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxkkAmM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxkkAmM.png&h=36293def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n住得咁近一直都無機會去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日學校請假 去試一試佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發！！"},{"pid":"9a2e39ad0f14ca583e38b8cdf6fd4330dc503567","tid":2335444,"uid":22856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"跟進中"},{"pid":"e3158ef51667c081f68b374e196650eec0476a01","tid":2335444,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81769e8e5e0df82429ff0e14d354b27fa3a12b25","tid":2335444,"uid":387795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2a287e5a54ce92b80023274bc41d3f6a68915c","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22