,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"巴打住日本？"},{"pid":"5d0a92453dfd05177f6cecdc75d9ad3f75bfc8c3","tid":2335444,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"Nihongjin？"},{"pid":"e0ec42597e855370409d4ae2d7aa3f7806cb5532","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1b456d2fc1f57bb1648594e54f658b7503ef9b","tid":2335444,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"烏冬唔係香川咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e82ca96baa9b33b3b32b9fb57ae1a8920ae9ce","tid":2335444,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"留名等相"},{"pid":"842ca788706e8f25c2c9b856eb1c9c7fa7d5601e","tid":2335444,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a07ce75c210932a18d941c3257c047dfd40d68f","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QkTV34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QkTV34.png&h=9cbd6c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x40QdQS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx40QdQS.png&h=fd40a7f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n排左大概20分鐘 終於入到鋪頭<br />\n<br />\n佢同時出左兩隻限定（Twitter每日更新）<br />\n<br />\n不過第一次黎到就食左招牌麵<br />\n<br />\n點左左上角既特製白醬油煮干+大盛<br />\n<br />\n最平既拉麵700円　算係好親民<br />\n<br />\n連續第四年獲得東日本（東京以外）百名店<br />\n<br />\n實力可想而知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6060c8864dad1b7ed2148dd6e9e68829f6a470ac","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"842ca788706e8f25c2c9b856eb1c9c7fa7d5601e","tid":2335444,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ec42597e855370409d4ae2d7aa3f7806cb5532","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1b456d2fc1f57bb1648594e54f658b7503ef9b","tid":2335444,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"烏冬唔係香川咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"我最中意食秋田稻庭烏冬<br />\n屋企附近有間退役棒球手既名店<br />\n<br />\nbtw仙貝呢 我要仙貝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6183968d135d61b1463393323e9bfcb493635b94","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"鋪頭入面闊落 一次過可以坐到20個客<br />\n坐低大概五分鐘 麵就來了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAZadTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAZadTb.png&h=64d3d0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n碗拉麵好靚 即刻飲啖湯<br />\n係醬油既清香 唔會過鹹<br />\n醬油以外仲有煮干既香氣<br />\n湯入面 醬油同煮干我覺得係7：3比<br />\n麵一咬落去好意外 係脆既<br />\n我本身以為係淋身 但佢竟然係似雲吞麵既硬度<br />\n麵有微微麥香 唔太掛湯<br />\n所以食麵同飲湯同步進行<br />\n碗前有一塊雞胸肉 口感一般 味道唔濃<br />\n而流血既係豬肉 口感軟淋 味道似火腿 有成四塊<br />\n成碗野最好食既竟然係蔥 埼玉出名大蔥<br />\n食落香甜 令我想起雲吞麵既韭黃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4WxbHMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4WxbHMC.png&h=c1fcf8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後係雞蛋 望落唔太濃味<br />\n但食落去 蛋黃非常濃郁 果然係對醬油有研究既鋪頭<br />\n估計隻蛋用白醬油浸到入味 幾好食<br />\n<br />\n總結呢碗麵物超所值 果然係百名店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5b3dd33d6b178ad318bbaceab679a90cd64cbd","tid":2335444,"uid":8203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"仲有荀 荀都好食 唔會太濃味<br />\n成碗麵做到個平衡 唔會喧賓奪主<br />\n每野樣都相附相成 完全做到「淡麗」兩個字"}]}